dc_title_s: Platte grondt de verbrande stadt London.
dc_description_s: Includes inset plan for a new city: "Modell der ab gebrandten stadt London new zu bawen", and inset view of the London fire of 1666: "Londons brandt". 1 map; 30 x 54 cm., folded to 18 x 14 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
